This information is interesting to me because I have always been a huge basketball fan.

very interesting if I were to gather data regarding past NBA Champions. I
found these data online through dierent websites. I wanted to nd associations
regarding awards that were given that year in regard to who the champions
were. This information is interesting to me because I have always been a huge
basketball fan.

In the rst function, I found what mean number of regular season wins was for a NBA champion. In the
second function, I found out what the standard deviation of regular seaason wins was for NBA champion. In
the third function, I found out what the maximum number of regular season wins was for a NBA Champion.
In the fourth function, I found the mean number of wins for the Lakers whent they won a championship.
In the fth function, I found the median winratio for every MVP Team. In the sixth function, I found the
winratio for championships in every MVP position which were guards. I also found that the Celtics had the
highest championship win ratio. The most wins for a losing team was 73 games in 2016. The least number
of wins for a championship team was 37.
